@startuml use_cases
!theme plain
title Wiki Publisher - Use Cases

skinparam usecaseBackgroundColor #E8F4F8
skinparam actorBackgroundColor #F0E8F8
skinparam arrowColor #333333

actor User

rectangle "Wiki Publisher System" {
  usecase "Configure Publisher" as UC1
  usecase "Parse Documentation" as UC2
  usecase "Transform Content" as UC3
  usecase "Connect to Confluence" as UC4
  usecase "Create Pages" as UC5
  usecase "Update Pages" as UC6
  usecase "Upload Attachments" as UC7
  usecase "Publish to Space" as UC8
  usecase "Set Page Properties" as UC9
  usecase "Handle Errors" as UC10
}

User --> UC1: Provides config\n(URL, credentials, mappers)
UC1 --> UC8: Triggers

UC8 --> UC2: Extract pages
UC8 --> UC4: Establish connection
UC4 --> UC5: Create pages
UC4 --> UC6: Update pages

UC2 --> UC3: Convert HTML
UC3 --> UC6: Apply transformations
UC3 --> UC7: Extract attachments

UC6 --> UC9: Configure appearance
UC7 --> UC8: Add to pages
UC9 --> UC8: Complete publication

UC8 ..> UC10: On error
UC1 ..> UC10: On error
UC2 ..> UC10: On error
UC3 ..> UC10: On error
UC4 ..> UC10: On error
UC5 ..> UC10: On error
UC6 ..> UC10: On error
UC7 ..> UC10: On error

@enduml
